<div>
    <h1>The Heretical Language Act</h1>
    <p id="body">
      This law criminalises the following ideas, lifestyles and beliefs: </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Capitalism</li>
        <li>Round Earthism</li>
        <li>The belief that birds are real</li>
        <li>Furries and furryism</li>
      </ul>
      <p>The following people are exempt from this law:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Those who follow those views due to a lack of knowledge</li>
        <li>Those who express those views satirically to ridicule them</li>
      </ul>
      <p>Those found to be breaking the law shall be sent to the gulag
    </p>
